### ─── Jikan (Uploader/Admin/Moderator) ───

### Search anime by title
POST {{baseUrl}}/jikan/search
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Tensei Shitara Slime",
  "limit": 10
}

### Current season anime
GET {{baseUrl}}/jikan/seasons/now?page=1&limit=15
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Anime preview by MAL ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/jikan/anime/20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Import anime by MAL ID (uploader/admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/jikan/import/37430
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
